Get more out of your laptop by giving it the resources it needs to perform.Simmtec designs, manufactures and resells computer memory modules. Simmtec started off brokering DRAMs and processors. In 1996, the company migrated to a memory module manufacturer which produced JEDEC compliant SIMMs and DIMMs. From 1996 on, Simmtec transitioned away from processors and focused more on memory; including proprietary, application specific and private label products. Simmtec has been an active JEDEC member since 1999.
